## 8. Reuse Notes

1. This schema documents the experimental data structure but does not permit reconstruction of the licensed Amap records.
2. Public QA pairs, prompt templates, KG schema, and evaluation scripts should use the same public field names and pseudonymization conventions defined here.
3. Any public artifact containing derived text must be regenerated after anonymization rather than anonymized through isolated string replacement.
4. Aggregate statistics should be checked against the final experimental dataset before release.
